<br>
Firstly, although they have undead nuke spells, a shadowknight cannot nuke undead.  The simple fact remains that SK's are biased toward melee and as such their spells are under level.  SK nukes simply cannot achieve the same kind of melee damage that can be achieved in the same cast time by a significant margin - maybe this changes at high level (my SK is 40th now), but I suspect not.<br>
